<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="sure-adv">sure <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ʃʊə(r), ʃɔː(r)/    美 /ʃʊr/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>[主要用于口语] 肯定地；当然：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Would you like to come? 
你愿意来吗？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Sure! 
当然愿意！</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>surely /'ʃʊəli/ adv [句子副词]  </p>
<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>— Can you show me Mr Jaffer’s office, please?
— <strong><em>_</em></strong>__. But I don’t know if he is in at the moment.   （2008 四川）<br />
A.Thanks <br />
B.Go on<br />
C.Sure <br />
D.You are welcome  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. C  </p></div>